In Concurrent or Sync modes, the "scheduler" module needs to be mocked to guarantee consistent behaviour across tests and browsers. For example, with jest: 
jest.mock('scheduler', () => require('scheduler/unstable_mock'));

For more info, visit https://reactjs.org/link/mock-scheduler

